Hurley MV(1), Walsh NE, Mitchell HL, Pimm TJ, Williamson E, Jones RH, Reeves BC, 
Dieppe PA, Patel A.

Author information:
(1)King's College London, London, UK. mike.hurley@kcl.ac.uk

OBJECTIVE: To conduct an economic evaluation of the Enabling Self-Management and 
Coping with Arthritic Knee Pain through Exercise (ESCAPE-knee pain) program.
METHODS: Alongside a clinical trial, we estimated the costs of usual primary 
care and participation in ESCAPE-knee pain delivered to individuals 
